title: 70. AITC: The Intersections of Music and Urbanism with Tanya Wells of Seven Eyes
itunes:title: 70. AITC: The Intersections of Music and Urbanism with Tanya Wells of Seven Eyes
description: This week, in our ongoing series Architecture in the Time of Coronavirus, we sit down with Tanya Wells of the musical act Seven Eyes to discuss the intersections of music and architecture. We ask about her catalogue of experiences during this global pandemic, the cross-culturality of their music, and her transnational upbringing that informs her craft now.
